data.description: Gorgeous single story property that is near city freeways. Home offers a great flow for family or to entertain or relax. You will love the patio and flex room that the home offers. Additionally the property offers high ceilings in the entry and also a built in bar, perfect for get togethers with loved ones. Very rare find to come across that offers both size & price.
